name: hiENS4
additional_notices: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: hiENS4 is an ERC-20 token representing 1/1,000,000 ownership of one 4-digit ENS in the ENS4 Meta-Swap pool of Fracton Protocol. For each 4-digit ENS added to the pool, the total supply of hiENS4 will increase by 1 million. In contrast, for each 4-digit ENS redeemed from the pool, the total supply of hiENS4 will decrease by 1 million.
